## posteo account ##

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User clara.kofler@posteo.com
# Uncomment one of the lines below depending on how the password is stored
PassCmd "pass Mail/clara.kofler@posteo.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.local/mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/posteo/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *

## webmail account ##

IMAPStore webmail-remote
Host imap.univie.ac.at 
Port 993
User koflerc99 
# Uncomment one of the lines below depending on how the password is stored
PassCmd "pass Mail/webmail"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore webmail-local 
Path ~/.local/mail/webmail/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/webmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :webmail-remote:
Near :webmail-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns *
SyncState *
